This site is created to record my studying notes.üìí 

The website is called wintersweet, the name of a flower that blooms in winter, which is also the English translation of my family name. I hope I can have one tenth of such toughness and courage in my lifetime, and bring some warmth to people around me.‚ù§Ô∏è
